{"type":"message","id":"3a81d461","parentId":"76581fa6","timestamp":"2026-03-16T18:07:00.643Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"创建 TOOLS.md","thinkingSignature":"1f50c0a3e84981c4dccd0ba31f86a4edb48d14225414223d2d08e2eacefcee35"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lydbkgpukkke_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# TOOLS.md - 小艺的工具箱\n\n继承全局工具配置，必要时可在此处添加自定义工具。\n\n## 常用命令\n\n### 磁盘分析\n```powershell\nGet-ChildItem -Path C:\\ -Recurse -File | Sort-Object Length -Descending | Select-Object -First 20\n```\n\n### 清理缓存\n```powershell\nRemove-Item -Path $env:TEMP\\* -Recurse -Force\n```\n\n### Adobe 缓存位置\n```\n%APPDATA%\\Adobe\\Common\\Media Cache Files\n%APPDATA%\\Adobe\\Common\\Media Cache\n%LOCALAPPDATA%\\Temp\n```\n\n---\n\n## 推荐网站\n\n- **壁纸:** unsplash.com, wallhaven.cc, Pinterest\n- **配色:** coolors.co, adobe.com/color\n- **灵感:** dribbble.com, behance.net, pinterest.com\n- **图标:** iconpark.com, flaticon.com\n","path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\xiao-yi\\TOOLS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":7321,"output":247,"cacheRead":34701,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42269,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773684415246}}
