{"type":"message","id":"bbac82ea","parentId":"6fbd7219","timestamp":"2026-03-16T18:17:45.093Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我把这个工作流保存到memory中，以便于未来快速查找。","thinkingSignature":"6192449241480a67a8c300d56490bccf4bd9785fd04bbcd577d793b32c33ac52"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_z43rra5p7hix_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 记忆库\n\n## Agent 创建工作流\n\n→ 详见: `AGENT_CREATE_WORKFLOW.md`\n\n### 快速摘要\n\n1. **命名**: 确定 Agent ID、名称、Emoji\n2. **创建目录**: `C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\{id}\\`\n3. **配置5个核心文件**: AGENTS.md, IDENTITY.md, SOUL.md, USER.md, TOOLS.md\n4. **注册**: 修改 openclaw.json 添加到 agents.list\n5. **配置触发**: 在 channels.*.routing.rules 添加关键词\n6. **应用**: gateway config.apply\n\n### 常用命令\n\n```powershell\n# 创建目录\nNew-Item -ItemType Directory -Force -Path 'C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\{id}\\workspace'\n\n# 查看现有 agents\ndir C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\n```\n\n### 已创建 Agent\n\n| ID | 名称 | 用途 | 创建时间 |\n|----|------|------|----------|\n| xiao-yi | 小艺 | UI设计师电脑管家 | 2026-03-17 |\n| interview-agent | 面试助手 | 面试/简历辅导 | 较早 |\n| design-pc-helper | Design PC Helper | 设计师电脑维护 | 较早 |\n\n---\n\n*更多记忆持续更新...*\n","path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\agent_admin\\workspace\\MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":17460,"output":349,"cacheRead":34701,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52510,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773685053048}}
