{"type":"message","id":"aa511029","parentId":"b8b4246a","timestamp":"2026-03-16T18:17:50.918Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"完成了！让我告诉用户。","thinkingSignature":"1a2f7c929c8c09faaa7fbed523119f9fb1bc6c42e947c3bdd0601d675e321440"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **已整理成标准工作流！**\n\n---\n\n## 创建的文件\n\n| 文件 | 作用 |\n|------|------|\n| `AGENT_CREATE_WORKFLOW.md` | 完整工作流文档 |\n| `MEMORY.md` | 记忆库（快速摘要）|\n\n---\n\n## 工作流核心步骤\n\n```\n1️⃣ 命名 → 2️⃣ 创建目录 → 3️⃣ 配置5个文件 → 4️⃣ 注册到配置 → 5️⃣ 配置触发词 → 6️⃣ 应用\n```\n\n### 快速要点\n\n- **目录**: `C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\{id}\\`\n- **必须文件**: AGENTS.md, IDENTITY.md, SOUL.md, USER.md, TOOLS.md\n- **注册**: 修改 `openclaw.json` 的 `agents.list`\n- **触发**: 在 `channels.*.routing.rules` 添加关键词\n\n---\n\n以后创建新 Agent 只需：\n1. 复制 `AGENT_CREATE_WORKFLOW.md` 作为模板\n2. 按步骤填写即可\n\n需要我演示用这个工作流再创建一个 Agent 吗？ 🚀"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":17851,"output":245,"cacheRead":34701,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52797,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773685065103}}
