{"type":"message","id":"f0ee5de3","parentId":"0751d727","timestamp":"2026-03-16T18:27:10.588Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户希望我维护一个agent注册表文件，并且把这个加入到工作流中。这样可以更方便地查看所有已注册的agent。","thinkingSignature":"e310a48f141c6b605aaffa3a7b7cc54f5ae82ed67a3b75a68599f1c5d4184c09"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_up6x393mf33i_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Agent 注册表\n\n> 所有已注册的 Agent 清单\n\n---\n\n## 当前 Agent 列表\n\n| ID | 名称 | 用途 | 触发关键词 | 状态 |\n|----|------|------|------------|------|\n| main | Main Agent | 主 Agent | - | ✅ |\n| agent_admin | Agent Admin | 管理员 | 创建agent, 管理agent | ✅ |\n| interview-agent | 面试助手 | 面试/简历辅导 | 面试, 简历, 找工作 | ✅ |\n| xiao-yi | 小艺 | UI设计师电脑管家 | 小艺, UI设计师, 电脑管家 | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n## Agent 详情\n\n### xiao-yi (小艺)\n\n- **路径**: `C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\xiao-yi`\n- **工作目录**: `workspace/`\n- **创建时间**: 2026-03-17\n- **性格文件**: SOUL.md\n- **工具文件**: TOOLS.md\n\n### interview-agent (面试助手)\n\n- **路径**: `C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\interview-agent`\n- **工作目录**: `agent/`\n- **创建时间**: 较早\n- **性格文件**: SOUL.md\n\n### agent_admin (Agent 管理员)\n\n- **路径**: `C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\agent_admin`\n- **工作目录**: `workspace/`\n- **创建时间**: 较早\n- **性格文件**: SOUL.md\n\n---\n\n## 添加新 Agent\n\n1. 在 `agents/` 目录创建新文件夹\n2. 配置 5 个核心文件\n3. 更新本注册表\n4. 执行工作流注册到配置\n\n---\n\n*最后更新: 2026-03-17*\n","path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\REGISTRY.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":60,"output":443,"cacheRead":52742,"cacheWrite":7686,"totalTokens":60931,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773685619498}}
